data.title: Blumenau railway station
data.meta_description: Blumenau railway station is a railway station situated in the municipality of RapperswilJona in the Swiss canton of St. Gallen. It is located on the Rapperswil to Ziegelbrcke line, and served by an hourly St. Gallen SBahn service S6 that operates southeast to Schwanden via Ziegelbrcke. Blumenau
data.text: Blumenau railway station is a railway station situated in the municipality of Rapperswil-Jona in the Swiss canton of St. Gallen. It is located on the Rapperswil to Ziegelbrücke line, and served by an hourly St. Gallen S-Bahn service S6 that operates south-east to Schwanden via Ziegelbrücke.
